  "texts": [
    "To gather other relevant papers, the concept of snowballing was used.",
    "Papers that did not principally focus on SR automation and explain the AI methodology used were excluded.",
    "The last update for the included articles was in 2024.",
    "From the search database, 21 new papers were added to the 31 previously recruited papers, resulting in 52 papers.",
    "Among these, 11 papers targeted the automation of the search phase, 33 addressed the screening phase, six focused on data extraction automation, and two on the automation of the RoB."
